    <div class="field field-name-body field-type-text-with-summary field-label-hidden"><div class="field-items"><div class="field-item even" property="content:encoded"><p>A few weeks ago, spurred on by some frustrating interactions with <a href="http://behat.org/">Behat</a> and Javascript, I started looking into alternative frameworks for running behavioral tests against Drupal. A little bit of searching led me to this helpful post <a href="http://www.phase2technology.com/blog/behavorial-test-for-custom-entity-using-casperjs/">Behavorial Test For Custom Entity Using CasperJS</a>, which outlines the basics of writing some simple <a href="http://casperjs.org/">CasperJS</a> tests for a site.</p></div></div></div>
